an actor like you for Rebel.

933
01:06:00,479 --> 01:06:01,855
I think...

934
01:06:02,559 --> 01:06:05,973
...divine fate calls the shots
for a director like me.

935
01:06:06,175 --> 01:06:08,031
You know what I mean? Brando.

