01:06:08,223 --> 01:06:11,835
What, are they kidding?
Brando is too old, man.

937
01:06:12,031 --> 01:06:15,862
You are fresh.
You are perfect for this part. Perfect!

938
01:06:17,183 --> 01:06:18,460
We just gotta...

