1000
01:09:29,534 --> 01:09:31,193
Are you all right, James?

1001
01:09:34,623 --> 01:09:35,605
Yeah.

1002
01:09:37,216 --> 01:09:39,833
We follow you in the newspapers.

1003
01:09:40,031 --> 01:09:43,194
